      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@\n+created: 2026-01-27\n+title: Improved Debug Output\n+intro: >-\n+  This release improves the debugging experience by making the `--debug` flag automatically\n+  enable verbose output, so you see all test results when diagnosing failures."
